## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources, which may reflect the biases of their authors. Additionally, the lack of access to certain archives, particularly Turkish military archives, limits the ability to fully understand the motivations and decisions of the Ottoman leadership. The ongoing political sensitivities surrounding the genocide also mean that interpretations can vary significantly depending on the source.

